<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">فِي التَّنْبِيهَاتِ:</span> شَرِكَةُ الذِّمم ثَلَاثَةُ أَضْرُبٍ:<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>